\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Well many a time he'd be - well be happen three - three or four days he might have been out three or four days or a week but it - never 
out long. He was always good - good workman and he always got - always could get a good job. Wherever he went he was - seemed to be well liked anywhere.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Your mother came from Rotherham?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Do you know how old she was when you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 She'd be - oh turned eighty.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 When she died?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Yes. I couldn't say what she were - how old she were when she were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid804774 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 . I couldn't tell you that. More than I know. I -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 How old were you when she died?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Me, oh - I should be - close on sixty. When she died.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did she have any jobs before she was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid804774 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 I couldn't tell you that, that's more than I can tell you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did she work after she was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid804774 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724  at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 No, I don't think she ever did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 She didn't have any part time jobs or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 No. No, mother never did that. Dad wouldn't let her do that. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Can you tell me something about your life at home when you were a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Well -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 About the house that you lived in in Clifton Avenue?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Well 
it was a - a nice - nice house and always plenty of freedom, me father never - upset us or anything. Never bothered with us. Only just to look after us and see we did what were right. But anything else - we mustn't do anything wrong. No, we he were very s
trict with us. Always kept us to our - in his place. Wouldn't - he wouldn't tolerate any cheek or anything like that. We had to do as we were told.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 How did he enforce discipline, how did he punish you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Oh yes, he - we used to get belt. Yes, he had - used to have a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10563220\charrsid15931724 belt}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 . We - we; used to taste it if we didn't do as we were told - and behave ourselves. Oh yes, he was very strict in that respect. Always be polite to }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid10563220\charrsid15931724 everyone}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 . And answer }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10563220\charrsid15931724 them}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 
 if they - were - asked us anything. Always kept within his place. Never got - we were all good and kind and - thought about his welfare more than anything.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did you feel close to him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Yes, oh yes, we were - we never were anything only our - go speaking if he were drunk. He used to like his beer. Yes, be
ing a miner they were all alike round - and we used to have to go and seek him sometimes. Come home many time - Saturday nights were his night out. Him and his pals. Mates that worked with, - they used to have a Saturday night out. On drink, boozing all n
ight. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10563220\charrsid15931724 And it's a thing as I never did do. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 I couldn't do that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 What about your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 No, she never drank. Mother never touched anything like that. She was too good for that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Do you know how many rooms there were in the house you lived in at Clifton Avenue?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Yes, two bedrooms and two }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10563220\charrsid15931724 downstairs}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Was the living room and a kitchen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Yes. Yes. There were kitchen and a front room. Front room and a kitchen. Two bedrooms.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did anybody else besides your parents and your brothers and yourself live there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 No. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10563220\charrsid15931724 No, there were nobody else, only us. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Only one family.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did your mother have any help in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 No, she never bothered nobody. Used to look after it herself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Was the washing done at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Yes. Mother used to do washing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did she or your father mend or make your clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Mother did, mother used to mend us clothes. She turned a thing like that. Me dad never bothered. Used to leave all to mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did she buy your clothes for you from a particular shop?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 
Yes. Oh yes, dad used to see to that. Not mother. Dad used to see to getting us clothes. If we wanted a suit he'd see that we got it. He was very good in that respect.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Was there a particular place he took you to to buy them from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 
Well I don't know, I couldn't tell you that - about that, where he used to go or what time - where he used to get them from. More than I could tell you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Would they be always new clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Yes, they were always new, they were never - anything else.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 How often did you have new clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 
Oh - two - I couldn't say - really say how often. I know we used to get Whitsuntide and - August Bank Holiday and Christmas for getting new clothes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 What about shoes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10563220\charrsid15931724 Oh dad used to have - to see to them. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 
Buy shoes for us and that. Oh yes, he was very good in that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did he help your mother at all with any of the jobs in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Oh he used to - they all had - to do his share. All brothers had to - got to do it. Used to fetch coal
, get firewood ready and - everything ready for mother putting on fire. We had to do that. Yes, we - we'd a good - good father and a good mother. Wonderful mother, mother more than father. Do with that a lot - a drink. Liked drinking but he was good.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did he do any cleaning or cooking or washing up to help your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Who, dad? Oh yes, many a time he's done it. For mother. Oh yes, he used to do it many a time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 What about decorating and repairs to the house, did he do anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 
Oh yes, do his own - windows and all that, with cleaning and everything as he could do he'd do it. Then we had to - we had to do the same, when we got old enough.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did you have particular jobs to do individually?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Oh yes, we had - yes, we had - 
one had such - such a job to do and done it for - youngest brother and he used to say - laugh at us 'cos we had to do it and he didn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did he never have to do any jobs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 No. Mother never bothered. She knew it'd get done when we get settled on.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 How long did you go on doing these jobs at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 'Til we were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid804774 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 
? I'd five brothers. Four more brothers and they all - they all - put their hand in and - until they were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid804774 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did your father do anything for you as children like dressing or undressing you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Or bathing you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Yes. Oh yes, father was very }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10563220\charrsid15931724 handy}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724  in house when he was in. He wasn't one to set down and watch it all being done by someone else. He'd do his share.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did he ever read to you or tell you stories?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did he take you out without your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Oh - he didn't - never bothered.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Would he look after you while your mother went out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Oh yes, he would. First thing he did was to look after us when we were younger.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Would he look after you while your mother went out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 
Oh yes. Oh yes. Mother went - wanted to go anywhere he'd look after us. He wasn't a man that'd - want to go his own way, he used to let mother have hers. Mother was - very god, me dad.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did you older children have to do anything to help the younger ones?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Oh yes, we had to help them to - get 'em dressed and do - do for them anything - anything we could do ourself we had to do it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did the younger ones do anything for you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Oh yes. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10563220\charrsid15931724 They'd}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724  come to us to - put their shoes and put their clothes on, dress 'em and wash 'em. Oh I done that m}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10563220\charrsid15931724 a}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 ny}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10563220\charrsid15931724  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 time. Me and me eldest - next eldest brother. Me and other brother. We used to}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10563220\charrsid15931724  look}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724  after them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did the younger ones do anything to help you?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Oh no. We never used to bother them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did you have to go to bed at a particular time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Yes. Oh we had to be in bed by a - eight o'clock every night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Was it your mother or your father who put you to bed when you were small?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 How old were you when you started putting yourself to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Oh - eleven years old.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 What were the sleeping arrangements, did you share the bed with anybody, or the bedroom?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 We had two beds, for - for - two big double beds and there used to be two in each bed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 That was in one room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 That were one room. Then father and mother had the other bedroom.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 There wasn't a bathroom?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 No, no, not that time of day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 What was the arrangement about bathing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Well we used to have 
a - a zinc bath and have a boiling water - put copper on that was in the kitchen, wash - where used to do washing, put fire in underneath and boil water in copper then put it in bath. That's how we used to work that, with bathing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Was it on a particular night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Oh yes, every Saturday night. Every Saturday night we had us bath.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Everybody?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 I don't know about father and mother, we didn't -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 I mean the children?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Oh aye, yes, oh yes. And Sunday School at Sunday morning. Up and off to Sunday school. Every Sunday morning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did you have your clean clothes to put on related to your bath night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Oh yes. Yes. Yes. Oh yes. Always plenty of clothes. Never short of clothes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Where did you have your meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Oh - the kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Were there any occasions when you ate in the front room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Well sometimes. In the - when they were - happen a birthday party. And we have it in the room but - very rare.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did your mother do the cooking in the kitchen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Oh yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Was it a fire?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Yes. Got a big oven. A - only a fire and oven. That's where she used to do all her cooking.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 What time did you have breakfast when you were a schoolchild?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Oh - in the morning about - eight o'clock. We had to be up early to g
et ready for school. And we used to have a breakfast when we started work we didn't used to bother with it - any. We used to go - take us snack with us and off to work for - be there for six o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Was that what your father did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Collier. He used to be up with us when we were - we were working only dinner.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 When you were at school, when you were having your breakfast at eight o'clock would he be getting up earlier and taking his with him?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Oh - mother. Mother used to be up early. Not fa
ther. Mother'd do - used to do all that. Look after us and see us off to school. But - not dad, dad never touched that. Won't let him have anything to do with it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Would he be at work then?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Sometimes. When he were on days he'd be at work but whe
n he was on afternoons - he' be in bed. You see. What they called days and afternoons at coal mine. He worked - one shift goes on at six o'clock - for six o'clock 'til two, the other }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10563220\charrsid15931724 
shift is}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724  afternoons, goes from two 'til ten at night. You see, that's - a
nd they used to change every week. Whoever on days this week from six to two well following week he'd be on from two 'til ten. You see, that - would happen like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 So the weeks when he was on from six 'til two would he get up very early?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 He'd
 get up by himself, he wouldn't bother nobody. He would put - he'd have a gas ring, put his kettle on, he'd get it and make himself a drink of tea and put his own snack, well, snack were put up the night before. Mother used to put snack up in his tin read
y for picking up and walking out. that's -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 So about eight o'clock there'd be you and your brothers and your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Oh yes. Oh she - mother'd be up then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 What sort of a breakfast did you have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Oh - just depend what we wanted. Never sho
rt. If we wanted egg we used to get it. If we didn't we used to have a - bread and jam or bread - plain bread and butter. We didn't used to be faddy or anything like that, just - all we got's bread and butter we were satisfied. Off to school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did you have a drink?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Drink of tea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 What about Sundays, did you have a special breakfast on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Oh yes. Mother used to get us breakfast special - Sunday morning. Sunday dinner too. Special dinner.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 What was that, a roast or something like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Make - makeshift dinners every day - we're going to school and - having about a mile to walk to school and back again.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 What do you mean by a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10563220\charrsid15931724 makeshift}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724  dinner?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Yes. Oh well - just depends what we had in house. If we had any eggs or -
 mother would fry us egg or - just depends what we wanted. It wasn't a case of what - she give us, it - what we asked for. She was very good. We asked for anything she'd get it.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 How many times during the week would you have meat for your dinner?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Meat? About three or four times a week. We were never short. Dad never see's us be short of anything we wanted. Nor mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 So for dinner you'd have,
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Just depends - ayes, what we wanted.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did you have a drink then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Yes. Always a drink of tea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 At tea time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Same. What - just what we wanted. Never barred from anything. Whatever we asked for we could get.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did your mother prepare different things for different people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Only - only for those in house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 If you and your brother wanted something different?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Oh yes, you could get it, oh yes. Oh she'd provide it. Oh yes. Oh they're very good, father and mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 You'd have a drink of tea then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Oh yes. Always have a drink of tea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did you have things like cake at teatime?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Yes. It just depends what they wanted.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did you have anything special on a Sunday for tea?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Yes. Well we - she used to make cake and different things - buns. Bake for us, or bacon - in the oven.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Was your tea a cocked tea or just a light meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 I - I couldn't tell you that.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did you have anything to go to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Just a drink of tea. Just a drink, we never bothered nothing to eat, only just a drink. Of - all of us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did your mother bake her own bread?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Oh yes. She wouldn't - wouldn't have bought}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9068327\charrsid15931724  bread.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724  Hers always bake. Always - see four stone of flour come every week. Yes. I wish her were here now.,.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did she make her own jam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Yes. She used to make it - lot of it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did she bottle fruit and vegetables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 And make }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10563220\charrsid15931724 pickles}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724  and things like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Yes. Used to do that a lot - do lots of things like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did she make any wine or medicines?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Oh no. Never bothered with wine.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 What about medicine?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Only da
d - he used to go to chemist, I think mother - and dad, they used to get theirs from chemist whatever we wanted. Not as they could make anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Was any beer brewed for the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 No. No, they never no beer.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did they grow any vegetables or fruit at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Yes. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10563220\charrsid15931724 Oh}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15931724  }{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10563220\charrsid15931724 
vegetables, I didn't - there were just one time we had a garden but after that he never bothered about it, always used to buy vegetables and - well things whatever she wanted, she never used - dad used to never - if you get g
arden he used to grow 'em, potatoes and cabbages and cauliflowers and that sort of thing but ; when he was - not working but when he were working he used to bother.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did the family keep any livestock, any hens or anything like that?
