\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 No, they didn't think it was wrong but they didn't - wouldn't allow us to play. Not at Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did they think it was wrong to work on a Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did they go to church or chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Sometimes. They hadn't much time to go anywhere when - on a Sunday with having five of us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 What denomination was it?
