\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Is that Wentworth Woodhouse?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did you go there as an organized outing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Yes. Used to go down and - she - park, a tremendous park full of animals, different kinds of animals. Lord }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid10563220\charrsid15931724 Fitzwilliam}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 . }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10563220\charrsid15931724 And always had permission - th
ey could get permission for them to down and - inspect - have a look around his - and it was a big estate you know. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 
Tremendous estate. Had all sorts - all kinds of animals in it. Deers, everything you can mention. Bar - lions and tigers. And }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10563220\charrsid15931724 there's}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724  enough when we were in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 What other social organized by the church did you take part in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Oh - not much, just used to go to church and - then have a game of football at Sunday night. In street.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did you belong to the choir?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 No. No, were never good enough for choir. I wanted to learn to sing first.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Was there a temperance club attached to the church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 I couldn't say whether there were or not. More than I could say that.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Was there any other club at all that you belonged to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 No. Not I'm aware of. Used to go Sunday school and - and roam about. Be - on the big estate, Wentworth, you could go round. }{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10563220\charrsid15931724 Geeseborough}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724  and that. That - that's a village close to Wentworth. And all - nice outings - woodland all round. a wonderful place there.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Was grace said at mealtimes at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 We had to do. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Was it you the children who said it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Yes. All us had to say grace.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Prayers at night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Yes. Just to go bed on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did you ever have family prayers all together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Oh yes. Yes. There were five brothers, father and mother, we all - beautiful. Well - I would like to see 'em again.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did your father take an interest in politics at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Not at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 No. His - his politics were a pint pot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did he not even go and vote at election time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Oh yes, he could vote.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 What party did he vote for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 I don't know, I couldn't tell you' what he'd vote for.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 What about your mother, did she vote?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 I expect she'd go. But I never known her - I've known her go once or twice but I never known her to be eager to go.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did she support any particular party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 I couldn't say, I couldn't tell you whether she did or not. I know dad used to - have one particular party, that were pint pot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 
In some places people used to feel that they might risk losing their job or losing their house if they voted differently from how their employer wanted them to.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Oh.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Would your father ever be subject to any pressure from his employers on politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Not as I know of. I couldn't say. I don't think there were employers }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10563220\charrsid15931724 
bother}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724  colliers with voting. They were more interested getting coal out than - politics. Getting it - to - for sale.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 When your parents weren't doing their work how did they spend their time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Parents? Well, mother used to look after house and keep it - keep it shipshape, father used to be cut - pint pot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did your mother have any interests outside the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 I couldn't tell you. I never - troubled. That's more than I could tell you about that, whether she had or not I couldn't say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did she ever seem to go out just to enjoy herself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Oh she - oh yes, she used to go out - father and her used to go out together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 What sort of places would they go to do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 
Well I couldn't - they might go to a theatre or - some - parties, some of their friends and that. She'd a lot of friends. And her sisters - my aunties.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 How many evenings a week would your father spend at home or would he always spend them all at the pub?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 
Oh - no, sometimes he'd be out - at home. Yes. He decided one bit to buy a piano and then get organ and we all used to - be at home together then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 How often would he go to the pub do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Oh about twice a week. Saturday night was - main night. Saturday night was his main night at boozing.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did he ever attend any clubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 No, he never bothered no clubs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did he take part I - any sport?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Oh yes, he used to like sport. He did, he used to come with us, me and brothers, we used to play for one team.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did he play as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 
No, he didn't play, he used to be - he used to come and see us everything was all right with us. Oh no, he - he wasn't a player like we were.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did he ever attend races or did he ever bet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 He had a bet now and again but I don't think he would do it regular.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9068327\charrsid15931724 
 It were only now and again, if someone}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724  told him a - name of a horse - he might have a shilling on and might - might not, just depends how he felt.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did he ever go to watch a race?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Oh yes, he used to go watch - sports and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 To watch a horse race?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Yes. He - they used to have a pit club, they used to have a day out at races. Doncaster racecourse used to go - that's where they -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Was that the holiday club that you spoke about?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 
Yes. The holiday club for the places used to go - boozer. He had a club there and he used to put so much a week away in then when it come race week they used to have a couple of days at races with this money as they'd all collected for year, you see.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did he belong to any other savings clubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did your mother belong to any?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 No. Not as I'm aware of.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 There weren't any savings arrangements for sickness?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 There were no savings - no, no there were no saving clubs-
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Funeral benefit or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 You say your parents made you and your brothers all get on well together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Was there any one of your brothers that you felt particularly close to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Oh - we never used to be - all }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10563220\charrsid15931724 alike}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 . All - never - no different to when we met.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 As a child who did you play with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Oh - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9068327\charrsid15931724 only}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 
 me brothers. I never bothered nobody else. We all used to go out together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 You didn't play with any of the neighbours children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 No. We should get into row if we did. Oh, we did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 You mean your parents didn't allow you to play with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Oh my parents didn't stop us. It was those parents who didn't - we weren't good enough to play with the others. W
e were poor - because we were collier - my dad was collier we weren't classy enough for them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 What were they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Office workers. Clerks and - bit of fal-de-lals. We weren't classy enough for them. It's the only time we used to get into a row if we 
- well we used to be friendly wi' 'em if they were friendly w' us. They parents }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10563220\charrsid15931724 sees us}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 
 talking to them they shout 'em away. Call 'em away from talking to us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 How did you feel about that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 What do you think. What you think about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did it bother you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Of course it did, used to think we weren't classed good enough for them. Make you feel underneath as if we }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid10563220\charrsid15931724 were no}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724  class at all.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did it bother your parents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 No. I don't know, they - me dad wouldn't talk to any of them. And I do
n't know - remember me mother talking to 'em and - as a matter of fact. They used to keep usself to usselves and - always cold }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10563220\charrsid15931724 shouldered}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 . They used to go - out of - out of way altogether to have games. Where it was peoples we didn't know. Then go out to play, but these'd stand there.
