\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Oh yes. For food and drink. Come walking in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Were neighbours invited in?
