\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did it go up a bit with each different job?
