\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 No. It was about - ten year we'd been }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid804774 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724  then. Then - and then - I was going to say, was only holidays - that was only holiday we had barring - war. There were no holidays then. When I were in Army.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 You were in the 1914/18 war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 In between your mining career?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Yes. I was in - I was signaller, linesman. Royal Engineers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 During the early part of your }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid804774 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724  life how did you used to spend your Saturdays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Oh we used to go out shopping together, me an
d wife. Go and do a bit of shopping. Go round market and - buy different things if we - anything she fancied.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did you go out on Saturday evenings anywhere?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 No, we used to sit at home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 How did you spend Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Oh we used to go to her mothers on a Sunday. Mother wouldn't - if we didn't go there'd be a row.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did you have special Sunday clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Yes. Oh yes, we had special clothes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did you think it was wrong to work or enjoy yourself on Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 No. No, it didn't matter to us. Being used to working at Sundays.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did you attend a place of worship then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 The same church was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Church. Church of England.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did you go regularly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Yes, every Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 What about your wife?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 She used to go as well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 You didn't belong to the choir did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Oh no. No, I never - never could }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7620559\charrsid15931724 be }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 professional enough to be in choir.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Were there any Church activities, any organizations or clubs or anything that you belonged to then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 No, there were no clubs, we didn't belong to any clubs. I don't believe in drinking, spending me time in there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 I meant organizations connected with the church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Yes, oh well, yes. Concerts and that. But - never anything else.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did you go to the concerts to watch?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Or did you actually take part in anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 No, we never took part, we used to go.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did you say grace at mealtimes, just you and your wife?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Yes. Used to say - grace.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Always?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Not often. Not always. Especially you've been working all day and you come - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Sometimes then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Sometimes we used to say it but - we were always ready to get down for my meals when you come out of pit.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did you have prayers together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Always together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did you take an interest in politics as you were growing up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 No. No I never took }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7620559\charrsid15931724 none}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724  in politics. I'd enough with seeing them and did - did take in politics.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 What about your wife?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 She were the same as em, she didn't believe in them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did you use your vote though?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Oh yes. Used to go in and vote. We used them. Just put persons as we wanted to be - to vote for. But as for anything else, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 What were your political views, what party did you support?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Labour.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 And your wife as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Yes. Labour party.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did you ever feel under pressure to vote for a particular party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did you ever take part in any political activities at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 No. No, I never did that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 You say in your leisure time you used to spend a lot of time reading?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Were there any other things that you did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Well - just - pass time away doing the different things, with writing and - planning things out and do - you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did you go out together in the evenings during the week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Sometimes. If we just felt equally to going out we used to have a walk round.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 What sort of places? You just went for walks?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Yes. No calling anywhere, just have a walk.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Were you working shifts in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Yes. Days, afternoons.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 How many evenings a week would you normally be at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Oh every - every week - one week every night evening. When I were on afternoons, used to go on at two o'clock 'til ten at night. So we -

\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 The week when you were on from six 'til two?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 We'd spend us evenings together in house. Or we might go for a walk in the evening. If it were fit.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did you go out very often?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Oh - oh yes, very often.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did your wife ever go to any clubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 No. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7620559\charrsid15931724 She never bothered with no clubs.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did you belong to any savings clubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Yes. Can't think of name.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Something like Oddfellows?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Insurance?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Insurance, yes. Belonged to insurance company. We had our savings in there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Was that for }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7620559\charrsid15931724 sickness}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 ? Or life insurance?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Yes. That was what - saved me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did either you or your wife ever take part in any sport?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Well - just a - with children yes, in the church - chapel sports. Church sports we used to go and take part in 'em.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 What was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Cricket, football. Bowling.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did you ever go fishing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Oh yes. I used to go fishing sometimes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did your wife come as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Yes. Never went without one another. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did you ever go out shooting?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Oh no. Be somebody shot through the leg if I had.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did either of you ever have a bet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 A bite? Bet? Oh many a time. I have to have bets.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 On horses was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 On horses.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did you ever go to the races?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Yes, Doncaster.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did your wife come there as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Yes, we both used to go there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did she used to bet too.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 No. You couldn't get her to put a - put a penny on a horse. She said, they're not going to win. They're not having mine.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did you go to any theatres or concerts?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Oh yes. Theatres and concerts.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Music hall or cinemas?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Yes. Cinema.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did you have any hobbies?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Boot repairing and - making different things from - brook called hobbies. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7620559\charrsid15931724 
We used to try and - our hand at making things with that. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 By fret work. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7620559\charrsid15931724 Fret working}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724  and that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 And your wife used to do it as well did she?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Yes. We both used to work together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did your wife have any interests outside the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Yes. Used to go out with - some friends of hers. All }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid804774 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724  girls. They all used to go out together in parties and that. When we were working.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did anybody outside the home help her with the house at all ever?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 What about if she was ill, how did you manage then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 
Oh - her mother used to come and see to her. If she was ill or anything went wrong we used to let her mother know and she'd be there. My mother would too. She'd be there as well. Anything was wrong with her.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 What relatives did you have living near?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 There was her father and mother, my father and mother not far away. Brothers and sisters, they lived round about the district.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 How much did you see of them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Oh - nearly every day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Was that because they came to see you or did you go and see them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 We used to go - we used to visit in us turns, one with another.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 What about friends, did you have friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 We was all friends next door and friends in street. They're all friendly together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did you visit one another?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Yes. Visit one another.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did you and your wife share the same friends or did she have some of her own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 And you have some of your own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 No, they were both together.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 When friends came into the house were they offered something to eat and drink?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 What about if they called in casually?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 
Well they - they just as - if they didn't want anything they didn't have to. We used to provide if they wanted - ask them. So they'd just pop in and - some of them just lived down
 street. They used to just pop in ask how you were going on and see whether she wanted anything. Same with our - with us }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7620559\charrsid15931724 with}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 
 them, for them, we used to pop in and see if they were wanting anything. And that's all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did you invite people in on special occasions?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 
No, I don't remember inviting - inviting anybody. They used to come without being invited. If they were anywhere near where we were they'd come and see us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Was your home rented there or did it belong to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 No, it didn't belong to us own house. The furniture did. The furniture - own furniture but -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 The house was rented?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Yes. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did you see anything of the landlord?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 The landlord he'd get it done. Wanted any repairs doing or anything like that. You'd have to report it to him. He'd have it done then.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did you see this landlord?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did I see him? Regular. He lived near - not far away. Oh he was - always knocking about.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Would you say that the community that you lived in at Parkgate was similar to the one that you'd lived in as a child or was it different?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 No different.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Was it a mining community?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Mining - part of a mining village. Stubbing colliery was close to it. Alder colliery was nearer than that.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 So that your community life would be very similar to what it had been before?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 And the composition of the people would be the same?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 You wouldn't have any specially important people living there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 No, no, there were no special - they were all miners and steelworkers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Did you have a struggle to make ends meet when you were first }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid804774 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 No, we - no, what we saved up and - helped us out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2378835 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Were you ever ill and off work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8937501 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 Not 'til after war, never had no illness 'til after war. Through being badly wounded got - caused me to have a lot of illness.
\par }\pard \ltrpar\ql \fi-461\li461\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin461\itap0\pararsid2378835 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3164241\charrsid15931724 
\par }}